==== 伊朗 ====
1979年[[伊朗伊斯蘭革命|伊朗伊斯蘭革命]]时，民众曾在晚间的屋顶高呼大赞辞，以示抗议。而在[[2009年伊朗总统选举|2009年伊朗总统选举]]后的[[伊朗綠色革命|抗议活动]]中，每晚22:00–22:30均有民众呼喊“真主至大”，以表达对选举结果的抗议。<ref>[http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20090614/ap_on_re_mi_ea/ml_iran_election Yahoo News]  {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090617072238/http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20090614/ap_on_re_mi_ea/ml_iran_election |date=2009-06-17 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9WU-cxEEJ-E |title=YouTube |publisher=YouTube |date=June 9, 2009 |accessdate=May 8, 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310145317/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9WU-cxEEJ-E |archive-date=2016-03-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/8386335.stm|title=How Iran's opposition inverts old slogans|date=December 7, 2009|work=BBC News|accessdate=December 21, 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100102053922/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/8386335.stm|archive-date=2010-01-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>

